    <string name="ambient_light_screen_title">Ambient light</string>
    <string name="ambient_light_info_content_description">Ambient light help</string>
    <string name="ambient_light_info_title">How it works</string>
    <string name="ambient_light_info_text">This section controls cabin ambient lighting — soft lighting on the panel, doors, and other zones.\n\nAuto — lighting turns on and off on your schedule. Set «Turn light on» and «Turn light off». The schedule runs in the background even when the app is closed or the head unit reboots. This mode is saved.\n\nOff and On — lighting stays always off or always on. The mode lasts until the app restarts. Next time you open this section, the app shows the vehicle\'s current lighting state.</string>
